file.content:
openapi: 3.0.3
info:
  title: zuzul-user-service
  description: zuzul-user-service
  version: 1.0.0
servers:
  - url: 'http://localhost:7990'
paths:
  #FINISHED
  /zuzul-user-service/v1/pub/image/user/{user-id}/avatar/{img-id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - Avatar of user
      description: 'Get avatar image of a user'
      responses:
        404:
          description: Not found
        200:
          content:
            image/*: # Media type
              schema:
                type: string
                format: binary
          description: Found
  #FINISHED
  /zuzul-user-service/v1/pub/image/user/{user-id}/cover/{img-id}:
    get:
      tags:
        - Cover Image of user
      description: 'Get cover image of a user'
      responses:
        404:
          description: Not found
        200:
          content:
            image/*: # Media type
              schema:
                type: string
                format: binary
          description: Found
  #FINISHED
  /zuzul-user-service/v1/user/profile:
    put:
      tags:
        - Update user profile
      description: 'Update user profile'
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                userId:
                  type: string
                userFullName:
                  type: string
                userEmail:
                  type: string
                userPhone:
                  type: string
                userBirthday:
                  type: integer
                userSex:
                  type: string
      responses:
        200:
          description: Update successfully
        500:
          description: Failed
  #TODO:
  /zuzul-user-service/v1/user/cart:
    get:
      tags:
        - List all item in cart
      description:  List all item in cart
      responses:
        200:
          description: success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: array
                items:
                  type: object
                  properties:
                    prdId:
                      type: string
                    purchaserId:
                      type: string
                    sellerId:
                      type: string
                    count:
                      type: integer
                    originPrice:
                      type: integer
                    prdSale:
                      type: integer
                    status:
                      type: string
    post:
      tags:
        - Add new Item to cart
      description: 'Add new Item to cart'
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                prdId:
                  type: string
                purchaserId:
                  type: string
                sellerId:
                  type: string
                count:
                  type: integer
                originPrice:
                  type: integer
                prdSale:
                  type: integer
      responses:
        200:
          description: success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  status:
                    type: string
    put:
      tags:
        - Change number of Item in Cart
      description: 'Change number of Item in Cart'
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                prdId:
                  type: string
                purchaserId:
                  type: string
                sellerId:
                  type: string
                count:
                  type: integer
                originPrice:
                  type: integer
                prdSale:
                  type: integer
      responses:
        200:
          description: success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  status:
                    type: string
    delete:
      tags:
        - Remove an item in cart
      description: 'Remove an item in cart'
      requestBody:
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              type: object
              properties:
                prdId:
                  type: string
                purchaserId:
                  type: string
                sellerId:
                  type: string
                count:
                  type: integer
                originPrice:
                  type: integer
                prdSale:
                  type: integer
      responses:
        200:
          description: success
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                type: object
                properties:
                  status:
                    type: string
